commit bba698eee684245245b71f6e5e4f9a40717e4be0
Author: Matijs van Zuijlen <matijs@matijs.net>
Date:   Wed Aug 25 00:28:14 2010 +0200

    Make rcov work when running metric_fu.
    
    Set metric_fu's config for rspec so it does not load tests under test/.
    This avoids loading the performance test, which made rcov fails since it
    needs the -Itest flag, and which we don't want to take into account for
    coverage anyway.

commit 5119a5d3bf9b961901ce49d21102a2fcb6155c92
Author: Matijs van Zuijlen <matijs@matijs.net>
Date:   Thu Aug 26 00:02:20 2010 +0200

    Update specs for Admin::ThemesController.
    
    - Remove needless boilerplate.
    - More rspec-like test descriptions.
    - Simple spec for :editor action.

commit a9b402f1e643d4cb515508247301d82552de3172
Author: Matijs van Zuijlen <matijs@matijs.net>
Date:   Thu Aug 26 00:02:52 2010 +0200

    Fix mismatched HTML tags in themes editor template.

commit 40986f23b403c00c76dbe152f2079918f29e74d9
Author: Matijs van Zuijlen <matijs@matijs.net>
Date:   Thu Aug 26 11:13:42 2010 +0200

    Also use untranslated string when translation is empty.
    
    The existing implementation only used untranslated string when the
    translation was nil. This does not match the actions of make_language.rb,
    which puts the empty string for unknown translations.

commit 7e411b15e41ac15539dd767037011338beaf941b
Author: Matijs van Zuijlen <matijs@matijs.net>
Date:   Thu Aug 26 11:25:05 2010 +0200

    Sort translated files by name.
    
    The dir glob for iterating over translatable files returns file names in an
    undefined order. This meant running make_language.rb would needlessly
    reorder items. The filenames are now iterated over in alphabetical order.
    This does mean there will be a one-time reordering when the translations
    are updated.

commit cfd4cd7e5f4dd69b3de69b51f7af3d794c5f7e8b
Author: Matijs van Zuijlen <matijs@matijs.net>
Date:   Thu Aug 26 11:36:50 2010 +0200

    Fix grammar error and associated translations.

commit 981f92d463e3b9217df9577395ce9f9ac51f0c69
Author: Matijs van Zuijlen <matijs@matijs.net>
Date:   Thu Aug 26 13:33:09 2010 +0200

    Update Dutch translation.
    
    Update the translation to match the order created by the recent change to
    make_language.rb, and to include all current translatable strings. Some
    obsolete translations were kept for later reference.

commit e6310f15fc9941b6d33a210c8c1835decbc188cb
Author: Matijs van Zuijlen <matijs@matijs.net>
Date:   Thu Aug 26 16:17:00 2010 +0200

    Keep obsolete translations when regenerating language.
    
    After outputting all current translations in file order, output any
    leftover translations in alfabetical order, so they are not lost but can be
    used for reference.

commit eeab76f1423806ced102bd35e1f7d3a4499554a5
Author: Matijs van Zuijlen <matijs@matijs.net>
Date:   Thu Aug 26 17:05:37 2010 +0200

