commit 51a71e04ea58d35141b79123265c50eb98ba0fee
Merge: 2764de7 a3038e7
Author: Matijs van Zuijlen <matijs@matijs.net>
Date:   Sat Sep 11 23:39:18 2010 +0200

    Merge branch 'master' into rails_3

commit 9baf4f3284ef674dc8d6de34fbff149369e9368e
Author: Matijs van Zuijlen <matijs@matijs.net>
Date:   Sun Sep 12 00:18:37 2010 +0200

    Rename AWS::Dispatcher::ActionController module to avoid error.
    
    Due to Rails' implementation of const_missing, the similarity of naming of
    ActionWebService::Dispatcher::ActionController to Rails' ActionController
    caused an error to be thrown: ``ActionWebService is not missing constant
    Base!''
    
    As a quick fix, the module is renamed to ActionControllerX.

commit 0a81817a3396e8466bafa14a92e7060d2464c916
Author: Matijs van Zuijlen <matijs@matijs.net>
Date:   Sun Sep 12 00:40:03 2010 +0200

    Change shared example specification.
    
    RSpec now uses shared_examples_for to specify shared examples.

commit 7c5ec3da6b3eaeb3038981cedf8efbbac84cb62b
Author: Matijs van Zuijlen <matijs@matijs.net>
Date:   Sun Sep 12 00:48:44 2010 +0200

    Remove replaced fixtures from global_fixtures list.
    
    Fixtures that were replaced by factories should not be in the
    global_fixtures list anymore, or else the fixtures loader complains it
    cannot find them.

commit d9f750c00816173dfcdd76f368e3fa45810bca01
Author: Matijs van Zuijlen <matijs@matijs.net>
Date:   Sun Sep 12 08:29:35 2010 +0200

    Increase spec nesting.
    
    - All specs now in describe AccounsController block, so no need for
      controller_name invocations.
    - Grouped 'with >0 users' specs.

commit efa0d855727adcbc9e6ad63630b60a90a31b640d
Merge: 7c5ec3d d9f750c
Author: Matijs van Zuijlen <matijs@matijs.net>
Date:   Sun Sep 12 08:30:00 2010 +0200

    Merge branch 'master' into rails_3

commit 85359b303842b291e5cf053516df7a65b0a6a97e
Author: Matijs van Zuijlen <matijs@matijs.net>
Date:   Sun Sep 12 09:44:09 2010 +0200

    Fix blog fixture's settings field.
    
    In Rails 3, you can no longer use nested YAML to set a serialized Hash
    field inside fixtures: You need to provide the actual serialized form.
    Hat tip to
    <http://code.alexreisner.com/articles/serialized-fixtures-in-rails-3.html>

