commit 3a5e8c2a2d19bf02be2d93d2ae40d98b18bb645e
Author: Matijs van Zuijlen <matijs@matijs.net>
Date:   Sat Sep 18 17:12:00 2010 +0200

    Use method.post? instead of comparing request.method.
    
    The use of request.method was broken since it does not return symbols
    anymore. Also, only the :post case was ever considered. So it's both a fix
    and a cleanup.

commit 106af20e975d9d4c6c7d658d9d4f47096c988fea
Author: Matijs van Zuijlen <matijs@matijs.net>
Date:   Sat Sep 18 17:22:59 2010 +0200

