commit 0d0c3b37b02f47b4562bdc3e8df1abaabaee253a
Author: Matijs van Zuijlen <matijs@matijs.net>
Date:   Sun Oct 10 20:40:44 2010 +0200

    Move or delete files from deprecated test mock directory.
    
    The use of the test/mocks/test directory is deprecated. Files that were
    used were moved from there to spec/support/mocks. These are required
    automatically. Unused files (theme_mock.rb and xmlrpc_mock.rb) were
    deleted.

commit d002689b630a024e242d96ff0b3b0b6a59b82312
Author: Frédéric de Villamil <frederic@de-villamil.com>
Date:   Sun Oct 10 21:44:14 2010 +0200

    Adds a way to use various database engines

commit bea6bf22a6f0f5f64dfcfc613def631ae7b56cfa
Author: Matijs van Zuijlen <matijs@matijs.net>
Date:   Mon Oct 11 20:10:55 2010 +0200

    Resolve bundler issues.
    
    By adding a group :adapters, but telling bundler not to load it, we can
    keep a uniform Gemfile and Gemfile.lock, but still load a different set
    of gems based on the database configuration.
    
    Also, the gems to load for databases other than mysql have a name that
    differs from the adapter names used in config/database.yml; therefore,
    explicitely map adapter names to gem names.

commit 07270b065eebc384e0da205f7181fa82f3077e73
Author: Matijs van Zuijlen <matijs@matijs.net>
Date:   Tue Oct 12 08:27:20 2010 +0200

    Remove metric_fu rake task, replace by metrical configuration.
    
    See http://github.com/iain/metrical

