commit 28d0295bd8dd4b4527747e4c3b60327a1064a9e7
Author: Matijs van Zuijlen <matijs@matijs.net>
Date:   Sun Oct 17 18:02:38 2010 +0200

    Avoid setting ENV["RAILS_ENV"] in Gemfile.
    
    The existing construct accidentally set the environment to 'development'
    before Rails had a chance to set it to 'test', causing several failed
    specs.

